LESTER, Respondent, v. WRIGHT, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. February 15, 1894.) Action by George Lester against William A. Wright. _

_ Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JX

No opinion. Order reversed, with $10 costs and disbursements, and motion granted, without costs.
